application.model

Class UserSetting

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.model.UserSetting

  • public class UserSetting
extends java.lang.Object
    Store all user setting and tasks processing logic including command line options's keyword and settings, required tasks for the application, required task for main tasks, main tasks' priority, default header for the csv file, and the usage message.

    • Nested Class Summary
